<div class="collapsible-block">
<div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">▼&nbsp;文档&nbsp;4370-1</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none">
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">▲&nbsp;文档&nbsp;4370-1</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-content">
<p><strong>文档名：</strong>文档 4370-1</p>
<p><strong>内容：</strong><br /></p>
<div style="text-align: center;">
<div style="text-shadow: 1px 1px 0 #b7b7b7;">
<div style="border:solid 1px #000; background:#dbf2ff; padding:5px; margin-bottom: 10px;">
<p><span style="font-family: Source Serif Pro; font-size: 150%;"><br />
不想再一直看着<strong>同样的风景？</strong></span></p>
<p><span style="font-family: Source Serif Pro; font-size: 150%;">想来点<strong>崭新</strong>的<strong>激情体验？</strong><br /></span><br />
<span style="font-family: Sniglet; font-size: 200%;"><br />
玩<span style="color: green"><em>Fun Slide</em></span>就行了！<br /></span><br />
<span style="font-family: Sniglet; font-size: 150%;"><br />
<span style="color: green">Fun Slide</span>代表了一种崭新的设想，它会带你走向比<span style="color: purple">梦境</span>还狂野的绝妙世界!<br /></span><br />
<span style="font-family: Sniglet; font-size: 150%;"><br />
<strong>无聊了？</strong> 哪为啥不试试几秒钟飞到巴哈马？<br /></span><br />
<span style="font-family: Sniglet; font-size: 150%;"><br />
来玩<span style="color: green">Fun Slide</span>！他就在<span style="font-family: Verdana; font-size: 100%;"><br />
<strong>[已编辑]</strong></span><sup class="footnoteref"><a id="footnoteref-3" href="javascript:;" class="footnoteref" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.utils.scrollToReference('footnote-3')">3</a></sup>，<strong>保证</strong>爽飞你!<br /></span><br />
<span style="font-family: Sniglet; font-size: 70%;"><br />
<strong>免责声明：</strong>Fun Slide不承担任何与现实终结和/或其他任何超维度现象有关的责任。<br /></span></p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
